				</div>
				<hr style="width:1004px; margin: auto;" />
				<div class="topcontent" style="padding-top:20px;">					
				<text id="txt" style="font-size: 16px;padding-top:10px;">Good Buy</text><br>
				<text id="txt" style="color:#8059FF;font-size: 12px;padding-top:10px;">BY VANDHANA</text><br>
				<text id="txt" style="font-size: 12px;padding-top:10px;">Good quality paperback print. Delivered on time</text><br>			
				</div>
				<hr style="width:1004px; margin: auto;" />			
				
				
			</div>	
